<section class="home-about">
    <div class="container-narrow">
        <h1 class="main-title">
            How I can help you drive higher quality leads and sign more cases
        </h1>

        <h2 class="section-subtitle">Who the heck am I, and why I can help</h2>

        <ul class="content-list">
            <li>
                I'm the Director of Paid Media at <a
                    href="https://webris.org/"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener">Webris: Law Firm Marketing Agency</a
                >. My team and I are currently managing $400,000+ a month in ad
                spend across Google and Meta ads with
                <a
                    href="https://webris.org/results/"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener">amazing results</a
                >.
            </li>
            <li>
                Previously I've worked at CAMG as a Paid Media manager managing
                over $200,000 in ad spend for some of the largest personal
                injury and mesothelioma law firms in the country.
            </li>
            <li>
                I'm actively consulting with marketing agencies to improve their
                legal ad campaigns from small solo criminal defense lawyers to
                large lead brokers.
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .home-about {
        padding-top: var(--space-12);
    }

    .main-title {
        font-family: var(--font-display);
        font-size: var(--text-2xl);
        margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
        text-align: left;
        line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .section-subtitle {
        font-family: var(--font-display);
        font-size: var(--text-xl);
        margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
        margin-top: var(--space-8);
        color: var(--foreground);
        text-align: left;
    }

    .content-list {
        list-style-position: outside;
        padding-left: var(--space-6);
        margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
    }

    .content-list li {
        margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
        line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .content-list a {
        color: var(--primary);
        text-decoration: underline;
        text-underline-offset: 2px;
    }

    .content-list a:hover {
        color: var(--primary);
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .home-about {
            padding-top: var(--space-8);
        }

        .main-title {
            font-size: 1.75rem;
        }

        .section-subtitle {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
        }
    }
</style>
